nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.models

Class Types

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.uu.cs.ape.sat.models.Types

  • public class Types
extends java.lang.Object
    The Types class represents the list of data types/formats (List<Type>) that correspond to a single data instance (e.g. to a single input or output).

    e.g
    Types printableMap is described with a pair: <Map_type, PDF_format>
    Author:
    Vedran Kasalica
